column5: My friend and I went out on Baptiste looking for some largemouth, we found none, but we did get quite a few smaller Pike, and a couple Smallies too. We only had a trolling motor on the boat so we were kind of limited as to how far from the launch we could fish, but we did alright.
Did you catch the same fish twice?  The sunset in the pike pic is nice...
At least you got some. Better than the white stripe.
Beauty report and pics daryl0815 thanks for sharing Leechman

good report, I fished Baptiste last week, we caught Pike, Pickerel and small mouth. Although we didn't catch any we saw a floating dead perch so they must be in there too. It was my first time on Baptiste.
